<!--modal unit-->
<div id="About" class="modal hide fade">
<div class="modal-header">
  <a class="close" data-dismiss="modal" >&times;</a>
  <h3><%= "About Bus Tracker" %></h3>
</div>
<div class="modal-body">
     
Bus Tracker is a web application for the DC Metro transit system.  Bus Tracker provides the most recent transit information available by polling the WMATA servers for Bus positions.  This allows riders to make the best informed travel decisions.

This project was completed as a requirement for the course CSci 6221 at The George Washington University.
